  "title": "Locum Pharmacy Technician (x10) #HMS",
  "description": "<p>Locum Pharmacy Technician (x10) </p><p> 6-Month Contract </p><p> $20/hour </p><p> Across Polyclinics</p><p> Why Join?</p><p> Flexible work schedule (4 / 5 / 5.5 days)</p><p> Gain experience across multiple areas </p><p> Working Hours</p><p> Mon–Fri:</p><p>• 8.00am–5.00pm or 8.30am–5.30pm</p><p> Sat (Alternate):</p><p>• 8.00am–12.00pm or 8.30am–12.30pm</p><p> Work Locations (Roving Role)</p><p>Bukit Merah | Outram | Bedok | Marine Parade | Tampines | Pasir Ris | Tampines North | Eunos | Punggol | Sengkang</p><p> Must be comfortable travelling and covering different clinics (not fixed to one site)</p><p> Job Scope</p><p>• Dispense medications & process prescriptions</p><p>• Support MDS & PILBOX services</p><p>• Tele-dispensing & Video Consult support</p><p>• Medication reconciliation</p><p> Requirements</p><p>Min </p><p> O-Level + Pharmacy Technician Certificate (MOH / PSS / equivalent)</p><p> OR Min Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science</p><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan </p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
